---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PostSidebar from '../../components/PostSidebar.astro';
import RefiCalc from '../../components/RefiCalc.astro';
const productSchema={"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": ["FinancialProduct", "Service"], "name": "USDA Refinance", "description": "Refinance an existing USDA loan to reduce your rate or payment.", "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "Stairway Mortgage"}, "areaServed": "US"};
const faqSchema={"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": [{"@type": "Question", "name": "How do I know if it's worth it?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Compare your break-even point to how long you plan to stay in the home."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What are the closing costs?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "They vary by loan size and lender; we provide a clear estimate for your scenario."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Will it reset my term?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "It can. We can model both a fresh 30-year and a shorter term so you can compare."}}]};
const breadcrumbSchema={"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://stairwaymortgage.com/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Loan Programs", "item": "https://stairwaymortgage.com/loan-programs/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "USDA Refinance"}]};
---

<Layout title="USDA Refinance | Stairway" description="Refinance an existing USDA loan to reduce your rate or payment." canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/loan-programs/usda-loan-refinance/">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(productSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(breadcrumbSchema)} />
  <nav class="container-page lp-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/loan-programs/">Loan Programs</a> <span>/</span> <span>USDA Refinance</span>
  </nav>
  <header class="container-prose lp-header">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-blue mb-5">Loan Program · Refinance</span>
    <h1 class="display-lg">USDA Refinance: Lower Your Rate on a Rural Loan</h1>
    <p class="lede lp-lede">Refinance an existing USDA loan to reduce your rate or payment. Guided by Jim Blackburn · <span class="mono">NMLS #1072866</span></p>
    <div class="lp-cta-row"><a href="/same-day-approval/" class="btn btn-blue btn-arrow">See My Options</a><a href="tel:+19549931625" class="btn btn-ghost">(954) 993-1625</a></div>
  </header>
  <div class="lp-main">
  <article class="prose-editorial lp-body" set:html={`<h2><b>About the USDA Refinance</b></h2><p>A usda refinance lets qualifying homeowners refinance their existing mortgage to better match their goals — whether that's a lower rate, a different term, or access to equity. As an independent broker, Stairway compares offerings across many lenders to find terms that fit your specific situation rather than a one-size-fits-all product.</p><p>Because every borrower's equity, credit, and goals differ, the right structure varies. The calculator below estimates your new payment and break-even point so you can see whether refinancing moves you forward before you apply.</p><h2><b>When It Makes Sense</b></h2><ul><li>Your current rate is meaningfully higher than today's available rates</li><li>You want to shorten your term and build equity faster</li><li>You need to access equity for a defined purpose</li><li>Your financial profile has improved since your original loan</li></ul><h2><b>How Stairway Helps</b></h2><p>We run your real numbers, compare lender options, and tell you honestly whether refinancing pencils out for your situation. There's no obligation and no credit pull to start the conversation.</p><h2><b>Frequently Asked Questions</b></h2><h3><b>How do I know if a usda refinance is worth it?</b></h3><p>The key is your break-even point — how long until the monthly savings cover the closing costs. If you'll stay in the home past break-even, it typically makes sense. The calculator above estimates this for your numbers.</p><h3><b>What are the closing costs to refinance?</b></h3><p>Refinance closing costs vary but commonly run a few thousand dollars depending on loan size and lender. Some costs can sometimes be rolled into the loan. We'll give you a clear estimate for your scenario.</p><h3><b>Will refinancing reset my loan term?</b></h3><p>It can — refinancing into a new 30-year loan restarts the clock. If building equity faster matters to you, a shorter term may be the better move. We can model both.</p>`} />

    <PostSidebar />
  </div>
  <div class="container-prose"><RefiCalc mode="rate-term" /></div>
  <div class="container-prose"><p class="lp-compliance mono">This page is for educational purposes and is not a commitment to lend or an offer of a specific rate. Loan terms, rates, and qualification depend on your individual circumstances and are subject to underwriting approval. Stairway Mortgage is a division of NEXA Mortgage LLC.</p></div>

  <section class="section-tight lp-final-cta"><div class="container-prose"><div class="card lp-final-cta__card">
    <h2 class="display-md">Is refinancing right for you?</h2>
    <p class="lede">We'll run your real numbers and tell you straight whether it pencils — no credit pull to start.</p>
    <a href="/schedule-call/" class="btn btn-blue btn-arrow">Talk to Our Team</a>
  </div></div></section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .lp-main { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 2.5rem; max-width: var(--container-max, 1320px); margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .lp-main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .lp-breadcrumb { font-family:var(--stw-mono, 'JetBrains Mono'), monospace; font-size:12px; color:var(--color-mute); padding-top:2rem; padding-bottom:1.25rem; }
  .lp-breadcrumb a { color:var(--color-mute); text-decoration:none; } .lp-breadcrumb a:hover { color:var(--color-blue); }
  .lp-breadcrumb span { margin-inline:0.4rem; opacity:0.5; }
  .lp-header h1 { margin-bottom:1.25rem; } .lp-lede { margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
  .lp-cta-row { display:flex; gap:0.75rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .lp-body { margin-top:2.5rem; }
  .lp-body :global(h2) { font-family:var(--stw-display, 'Fraunces'), Georgia, serif; font-variation-settings:"opsz" 96; font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.25rem); line-height:1.15; margin-top:3rem; margin-bottom:1.1rem; }
  .lp-body :global(h3) { font-family:var(--stw-display, 'Fraunces'), Georgia, serif; font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2vw,1.55rem); margin-top:2rem; margin-bottom:0.8rem; }
  .lp-body :global(p) { font-size:17px; line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:1.25rem; color:var(--color-ink-light); }
  .lp-body :global(ul) { margin:0 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem; }
  .lp-body :global(li) { font-size:17px; line-height:1.65; }
  .lp-body :global(a) { color:var(--color-blue); text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:2px; }
  .lp-compliance { font-size:11px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--color-mute); padding:1.5rem 0; border-top:1px solid var(--color-bone); margin-top:2rem; letter-spacing:0.01em; }
  .lp-final-cta__card { text-align:center; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:1rem; padding:2.5rem; }
</style>
